# Dev-watcher excludes. The running app writes its history store + tile cache
# under src-tauri/data/, which sits inside the crate dir Tauri's `tauri dev`
# watches — every write triggered a full app restart (infinite rebuild loop).
# These are runtime data, never source, so exclude them from the watcher.
data/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
tilecache/
